    "Impacts the design of quantum experiments and technology"
  ],
  "common_misconceptions": [
    {
      "misconception": "Observer effect",
      "clarification": "Often confused with the observer effect, but the uncertainty principle is a more fundamental concept independent of measurement disturbance"
